00:00:58.080 --> 00:00:59.880
beginning in verse number one of Psalm 78.

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:02.680
Give ear, O my people, to my law.

00:01:02.680 --> 00:01:06.419
Incline your ears to the words of my mouth.

00:01:06.419 --> 00:01:08.319
I will open my mouth and a parable

00:01:08.319 --> 00:01:11.120
I will utter dark sayings of old,

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:13.459
which we have heard and known

00:01:13.459 --> 00:01:15.839
and our fathers have told us.

00:01:15.839 --> 00:01:17.680
Notice verse number four.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:20.839
We will not hide them from their children,

00:01:20.839 --> 00:01:24.040
showing to the generation to come

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:27.599
the praises of the Lord and his strength

00:01:27.639 --> 00:01:30.440
and his wonderful works that he hath done.

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:33.160
For he established a testimony in Jacob

00:01:33.160 --> 00:01:35.319
and appointed a law in Israel,

00:01:35.319 --> 00:01:37.279
which he commanded our fathers

00:01:37.279 --> 00:01:40.000
that they should make them known to their children,

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.160
that the generation to come might know them,

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:44.440
even the children which should be born,

00:01:44.440 --> 00:01:47.440
who should arise and declare them to their children,

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:49.879
that they might set their hope in God

00:01:49.879 --> 00:01:52.160
and not forget the works of God,

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:54.120
but keep his commandments.

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:55.800
It might not be as their fathers,

00:01:55.800 --> 00:01:58.120
a stubborn and rebellious generation,

00:01:58.120 --> 00:02:00.800
a generation that set not their heart aright

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:05.199
and whose spirit was not steadfast with God.

00:02:05.199 --> 00:02:06.519
In verse number four,

00:02:06.519 --> 00:02:08.039
and then again in verse number six,

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:12.119
you see that phrase, the generation to come.

00:02:12.119 --> 00:02:13.399
As I mentioned already,

00:02:13.399 --> 00:02:16.199
I am thankful for the generation to come.

00:02:16.199 --> 00:02:18.880
I am also thankful for those that God has equipped

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:22.080
and called to work with the future generation.

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:24.199
This evening, as we begin to think about the children

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:26.320
