I want you to understand

00:05:04.799 --> 00:05:07.200
that those that are in opposition to God,

00:05:07.200 --> 00:05:09.679
those that are in opposition to the word of God,

00:05:09.679 --> 00:05:11.799
they are actively engaged

00:05:11.799 --> 00:05:14.679
on seeking to reach the next generation.

00:05:14.679 --> 00:05:17.959
And not reach the next generation like we talk about.

00:05:17.959 --> 00:05:19.899
We talk about reaching the next generation

00:05:19.899 --> 00:05:21.640
for the cause of Christ

00:05:21.640 --> 00:05:23.760
and to influence them with the word of God,

00:05:23.760 --> 00:05:26.380
but we find that there's a group of people

00:05:26.380 --> 00:05:28.660
that are on our earth today

00:05:28.660 --> 00:05:30.519
that are the workers of iniquity,

00:05:30.519 --> 00:05:31.720
that are false teachers,

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:35.640
that are seeking to capture this future generation.

00:05:35.640 --> 00:05:37.720
They're seeking to indoctrinate them.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:40.579
They're seeking to develop their philosophy

00:05:40.579 --> 00:05:42.000
and their worldview.

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:46.600
And we must be aware of this battle that is raging.

