00:07:17.859 --> 00:07:22.859
And that's what I think we have an obligation to do.

00:07:24.839 --> 00:07:25.679
Wow.

00:07:26.799 --> 00:07:27.640
Wow.

00:07:29.279 --> 00:07:31.559
And we understand this evening,

00:07:31.559 --> 00:07:33.380
the battle that is raging.

00:07:33.380 --> 00:07:35.459
Some of us at a higher level than others.

00:07:35.459 --> 00:07:37.940
Some are more aware, some have children,

00:07:37.940 --> 00:07:40.140
and you see firsthand what's taking place

00:07:40.140 --> 00:07:42.260
and how the system that we're in,

00:07:42.260 --> 00:07:44.980
the culture that we're in is seeking to influence them

00:07:44.980 --> 00:07:47.040
and seeking to steal their hearts

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:49.380
and to give them a different worldview.

00:07:49.380 --> 00:07:52.739
And we look at that quote that it said there

00:07:52.739 --> 00:07:54.179
