00:08:18.959 --> 00:08:23.619
And we find that the influence of this society

00:08:23.619 --> 00:08:26.940
upon a future generation is given to us,

00:08:26.940 --> 00:08:28.920
and they've put these things in writing,

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.899
