00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:10.119
so that they know exactly what is being taught

00:09:10.119 --> 00:09:14.880
and how they are going to indoctrinate a future generation.

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:16.619
And so what do we do about that?

00:09:16.619 --> 00:09:19.440
When we think about a generation to come,

00:09:19.440 --> 00:09:21.520
some have had this perspective,

00:09:21.520 --> 00:09:24.840
I see the need, I see that there's a departure,

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:27.440
but I just don't know what to do.

00:09:27.460 --> 00:09:29.900
