00:10:53.379 --> 00:10:56.799
Begin to think about

00:10:56.799 --> 00:10:58.999
these statements in verse 4 and 5

00:10:58.999 --> 00:11:01.879
and thinking about the active engagement

00:11:01.879 --> 00:11:03.579
that is required

00:11:03.579 --> 00:11:06.119
of not hiding them from their children,

00:11:06.119 --> 00:11:08.759
of making them known to their children.

00:11:08.759 --> 00:11:10.999
It takes work.

00:11:10.999 --> 00:11:12.339
It takes discipline.

00:11:12.339 --> 00:11:15.339
It requires that we are strategic

00:11:15.339 --> 00:11:16.619
about what we're doing

00:11:16.619 --> 00:11:18.979
and how we're approaching

00:11:18.979 --> 00:11:21.259
the subject at hand.

00:11:21.259 --> 00:11:23.259
And this evening, I'd like to consider

00:11:23.259 --> 00:11:25.619
