00:11:25.619 --> 00:11:29.479
Number one, consider our responsibility.

00:11:29.479 --> 00:11:31.039
Consider our responsibility.

00:11:31.039 --> 00:11:32.559
It says in verse 4,

00:11:32.559 --> 00:11:34.579
we will not hide them from their children.

00:11:34.579 --> 00:11:36.399
And then notice the rest of the verse.

00:11:36.399 --> 00:11:38.879
